  "narrative_arc": "One day in a Paris banlieue where police shoot a boy with a rubber bullet and a drone captures it on video. Ly documents the parallel governance structures — police, mosque leaders, community bosses, and drug dealers all compete for authority in a housing project the state has abandoned.",
